---
title: Italian-Style Meatballs with Israeli Couscous, Wilted Spinach and Parmesan
description: This quick and easy meatball dinner is going to be a family favourite. Italian sausage meatballs in a rich tomato sauce sit over tiny pasta called Israeli Couscous. A sprinkle of parmesan and voila, dinner is served!
